      "type": "Term",
      "front": "Jay's Treaty",
      "back": "Jay's Treaty contained no British concessions on impressment or the rights of American shipping. Ultimately, Jay's Treaty sharpened political divisions in the United States and led directly to the formation of an organized opposition party.",
      "hint": "Jay's Treaty contained no British concessions on impressment or the rights of American shipping.",
