      "type": "Term",
      "front": "Political Parties",
      "back": "But the rise of political parties seeking to mobilize voters in hotly contested elections, the emergence of the \"self-created societies,\" the stirrings of women's political consciousness, and even armed uprisings like the Whiskey Rebellion broadened and deepened the democratization of public life set in motion by the American Revolution.",
      "hint": "But the rise of political parties seeking to mobilize voters in hotly contested elections, the emergence of the \"self-created societies,\" the stirrings of women's political consciousness, and even armed uprisings like the Whiskey Rebellion broadened and deepened the democratization of public life set in motion by the American Revolution.",
